19C26BDA.Line223.142AC2: Don't run! Don't hide from the likes of Hell! We shall break the waves of blood!

1DA29992.Line195.142B31: Serpent, root, tree, and whisper! Hear my call! The demons' fire is spreading!

30C987E9.Line203.142B32: Come out, everyone! Look up! Let the blood wash over you!

34A9B7A4.Line175.142B2F: Blood gathers in the sky, and the Father's warning rings in our ears! Our judgment is at hand!

3F462E6E.Line237.142B30: Trust in the merchants and their brave fighters! They'll fend off the demons...all will be well!

54FCED37.Line220.142AC2: Let the bastard devils come! All that burns shall grow again! Taller, stronger, unrelenting!

5A2D7C15.Line189.142B31: Hell steps upon the scale! The balance is tipped toward the abyss!

6C040946.Line200.142B32: (laugh) The Mother was right! Bleeding sky, soaking sands! Listen for the screams!

6FE43901.Line172.142B2F: The Burning Hells draw near! Cast aside your decadent ways! Repent!

7A80AFCB.Line234.142B30: We have dealt with Hell's fire before! Mount Civo did not take us and neither will this!

9187CFBA.Line214.142AC2: Hell is coming, my kindred! Brace like stone! Stand as oak! The 'Glen will prevail!

9567FD72.Line186.142B31: The waters run red, choking the swamp! A price must be paid!
